==English==
===Adverb===
'''[[by]] [[the]] [[way]]'''
#{{idiom}} [[incidentally|Incidentally]]; not [[central]] or [[crucial]] to the topic at hand.
#:''His mother will be coming for dinner tomorrow, and '''by the way''', she volunteered to bring dessert.''

